snippet.title: Calmed by the Dark Aftermath - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Release Date: 9 / December / 2020
Calmed by the Dark Aftermath is a Open-World Action-RPG set 4 years after a catastrophic event happened. Kadmos is looking for redemption and is up to you what his fate is going to be!
